# Netlify Redirects
# Serve rsvp.html directly at /rsvp.html without stripping extension
# This preserves query params (guest_id, name, tel) on the URL
/rsvp.html  /rsvp.html  200!
/rsvp       /rsvp.html  200
# Preserve query params on pdf.html (convite com link de confirmação)
/pdf.html   /pdf.html   200!
/pdf        /pdf.html   200
